cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image analysis and deep learning techniques to extract information from food packaging photos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of domain adaptation techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of information retrieval techniques to extract information from food packaging, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. Finally, the paper involves the use of multimedia techniques to analyze food packaging photos, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely category.
